OL,3,CSignal jammers and oath swearing: How
OL,4,Cthe secrecy of the Conclave is enforced
OL,6,FAt 3pm local time (2pm GMT) on
OL,7,FWednesday, the Vatican activated
OL,8,Fsignal jammers around the Sistine
OL,9,FChapel to block and prevent any
OL,10,Foutside communication or surveillance
OL,11,Fduring the conclave.
OL,13,FThe jammers block mobile phone
OL,14,Fsignals, preventing calls, texts, as
OL,15,Fwell as internet access. A similar
OL,16,Fsystem was used in 2013, when Pope
OL,17,FFrancis was elected.
