OL,3,CSignal jammers and oath swearing: How
OL,4,Cthe secrecy of the Conclave is enforced
OL,6,FThe blackout begins just 90 minutes
OL,7,Fbefore cardinals enter the Sistine
OL,8,FChapel to begin the papal conclave,
OL,9,FItalian state broadcaster RAI reported
OL,10,Fon Monday.
OL,12,FElectronic devices banned
OL,14,FCardinals handed over their mobile
OL,15,Fphones and electronic devices upon
OL,16,Fentering the chapel.
OL,18,FThese will only be returned once the
OL,19,Fconclave ends, ensuring there is no
OL,20,Foutside contact or influence during
OL,21,Fthe vote.
