OL,3,CSignal jammers and oath swearing: How
OL,4,Cthe secrecy of the Conclave is enforced
OL,6,FCardinals must take an oath of secrecy
OL,8,FAll cardinals taking part in the
OL,9,Fconclave will be in complete isolation
OL,10,Fand will swear an oath to observe
OL,11,F"absolute and perpetual secrecy".
OL,13,FThe first task is for the cardinals to
OL,14,Ftake the oath: "And I, (first name)
OL,15,FCardinal (last name), do promise,
OL,16,Fpledge, and swear. So help me God and
OL,17,Fthese Holy Gospels which I touch with
OL,18,Fmy hand," each cardinal recites in
OL,19,Forder of seniority.
