OL,3,CSignal jammers and oath swearing: How
OL,4,Cthe secrecy of the Conclave is enforced
OL,6,FThe Sistine Chapel is placed under
OL,7,Ftotal lockdown during the conclave to
OL,8,Fensure complete secrecy.
OL,10,FTight Security in St Peter's Square
OL,12,FThe signal jammers will not affect St
OL,13,FPeter's Square, so the public will
OL,14,Fstill have a mobile signal.
OL,16,FHowever, security has been stepped up,
OL,17,Fwith checkpoints at entrances, metal
OL,18,Fdetectors, and anti-drone systems in
OL,19,Fplace, according to news outlet
OL,20,FCorriere della Sera.
